{"id":7006,"content":"<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">中国共产党究竟成立在哪一年<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>这个中国共产党历史<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中国近现代历史中的重大问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>半个多世纪以来没有科学正确的解决<SPAN lang=EN-US>.2002</SPAN>年中共中央党史研究室著<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中央党史出版社出版的<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党历史<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>权威本<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>只承认<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立了上海共产党早期组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>也认定它是中共的第一个党组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>但不承认这是中国共产党的成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>笔者热心研究中共历史数十年<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>对自己加入的中国共产党何时成立当然很感兴趣<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>从收到朋友赠送的这套党史书起就想写一篇与此书此问题不同观点的考证文章<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>为此一直准备了<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>才下决心拿出此文<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>请史界的专家学者们评论<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>希望把这个题目的学术争论坚持下去<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>对立的观点都能得到发表<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>至于全党能否承认<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>当然还是全靠中央党史研究机构努力工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>全靠中国共产党的代表大会作出新的决定<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">一<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>用什么标准判断中国共产党的正式成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">我们研究中国共产党的成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>必须有个衡量标准<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这个标准是判断党成立的基本条件和根本依据<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>如果没有这个标准<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>就会出现谁说谁有理的真假不分的局面<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有碍于信史的形成<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>笔者认为这个标准应当这样<SPAN lang=EN-US>:&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">第一<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp; </SPAN>党的成立首先在于有组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>没有组织的单个共产主义者不是党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>没有组织的共产主义者伙伴也不是党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>有组织当然就有队伍<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有领导<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有组织活动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>有了组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>无论组织大小强弱<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>都标志党是个实体<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是客观存在<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">第二<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>党是有目的有纲领的政治集团<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>它与马克思主义学会或共产主义学会不同<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>学会的职能是学习讨论问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有组织而无政治行动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>一个学会只有在树立自己政治目的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>制定出政治行动纲领时才可以叫政党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">第三<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>党的成立一般都被当时的政治势力所公认<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>党是政治势力<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>政治集团<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>党的成立是社会上最敏感的问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>无论怎么搞地下工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>地上的政治势力都会知道你这个政党存在<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>国内外的政治势力极其关注政党的存在及其活动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>特别<SPAN lang=EN-US>1919</SPAN>年列宁建的共产国际<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>尤其关注和支持各国共产党的建立<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">第四<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp; </SPAN>党的成立一般都制定宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>党的成立宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是党的目的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>任务<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>纲领<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>步骤<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>手段和要求的通告<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>表示党的正式性和庄严性<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>具有誓师之意义<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">笫五<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp; </SPAN>党的成立一般都办个报刊<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>作为思想宣传阵地<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>如党的活动是密秘的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>党报党刊也是密秘的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>用党报党刊解释党的理论<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>路线<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>方针<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>政策<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>用以统一全党思想<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>以便步调一致<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">笔者认为<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>以上五条标准<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>用于判断中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年是否成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是最合适的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">二<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>中国共产党于<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立的原始档案文献的证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">原始档案文献反映的是中国共产党成立的素质特征和本来面目<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是考证中国共产党成立问题的最有力的客观依据<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>笔者引以下原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1,&nbsp;&nbsp; <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1920\" Month=\"6\" Day=\"17\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1920<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年6</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月17</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US>至<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2009\" Month=\"7\" Day=\"25\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">7<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月25</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US>的&lt;&lt;</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">俞秀松烈士日记<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&nbsp; &lt;1&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">俞秀松在<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2009\" Month=\"6\" Day=\"19\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>19</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>写到<SPAN lang=EN-US>:&nbsp; \"</SPAN>存统这天晚上乘船赴日本<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"</SPAN>他在<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2009\" Month=\"7\" Day=\"10\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>写道<SPAN lang=EN-US>:\"</SPAN>前回我们所组织了社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"</SPAN>我们看<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>俞秀松在语言上表达很清楚<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他的日记<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>说明<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>曰前<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>已经组织了党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>党叫什么名<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>叫社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>存统赴曰怎么回事<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>施存统要去日本留学<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这天<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>党纲起草完了<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>开会通过<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>施存统抄一份带去曰本<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>陈公培去法国勤工俭学也抄一份带去<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>俞秀松日记表明<SPAN lang=EN-US>,1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月间中国共产党就正式筹备和创建了<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>日记发现很晚<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>但它正好认证了施存统<SPAN lang=EN-US>1956</SPAN>年的回忆<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>俞秀松日记是原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月间有组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有目的有纲领的中国共产党开始创建了<SPAN lang=EN-US>!<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">陈独秀<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1920\" Month=\"9\" Day=\"1\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>在<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>新青年<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>第<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>卷<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>号发表的<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>对时局的我见<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&lt;2&gt;123<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">陈独秀此时己经被选为中国共产党的书记<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>此文似他个人见解<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>其实这是代表中国共产党的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>陈独秀在文中写道<SPAN lang=EN-US>:\"</SPAN>吾党虽不像无政府党否认政治组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>也绝不屑于学德国社会民主党<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>利用资产阶级的政治机关和权力<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>做政治活动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"</SPAN>陈独秀这里说的<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>吾党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\",</SPAN>既区别于无政府党<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>又区别于第二国际德国社会民主党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>那么他指的是什么党呢<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>陈独秀说的<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>吾党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>就是俞秀松曰记中写的<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>这个党的政治主张是什么<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>陈独秀在<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>新青年<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>第<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>卷<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>号发表的另一篇文章<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>谈政治<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>作了阐释<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>就是<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>我承认用革命的手段建设劳动阶级<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>即生产阶级<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>的国家<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>创造那禁止对内对外一切掠夺的政治法律<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>为现代社会第一须要<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"&nbsp; </SPAN>显然<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>这是走苏俄道路<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>即无产阶级革命无产阶级专政的道路<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1920</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月至<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>陈独秀建党时<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中国共产党这名字已经产生<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>但还没有最后定下来<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"</SPAN>社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>只是临时叫法<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>也没统一<SPAN lang=EN-US>..</SPAN>张国焘<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月中旬到上海办事<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>住在陈独秀家<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>多次与陈独秀讨论建党问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>陈独秀对党名没自已定<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>而是给张申府写信<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>叫张国焘捎给张申府<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>又叫张申府找李大钊说明情况<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>由李大钊张申府决定党的名称<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>张国焘<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>月下旬回北京<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>还没等李大钊张申府来信呢<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>陈独秀就在<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>曰发表这两篇文章<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>当然他说的<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>吾党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>就是俞秀松曰记写的<SPAN lang=EN-US>\".</SPAN>社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">这个<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>的提法<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>也被<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>16</SPAN>曰<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>申报<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>上的消息所认证<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>消息说<SPAN lang=EN-US>:\"</SPAN>社会党陈独秀来沪勾结俄党与刘鹤林<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>在法租界组织机器工会并刊发杂志<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>鼓吹社会主义<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>己饬军警严禁<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>可见<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>成立党的事<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>再密秘也会被政治势力所发现<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>这从反面认证了陈独秀文中说的<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>吾党<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>就是指<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>社会共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.&nbsp; 1920</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月制定的<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">这是宣告中国共产党正式成立的宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>是原始档案文件<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>但没有公开发表过<SPAN lang=EN-US>.1956</SPAN>年这个由苏联共产党中央移交过来的中文稿<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;,</SPAN>是根据英译稿还原的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>译者姓张<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他在<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>前面加一段说明<SPAN lang=EN-US>:&nbsp;\" </SPAN>亲爱的同志们<SPAN lang=EN-US>!</SPAN>这个宣言是中国共产党在去年<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月间决定的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这宣言的内容不过是关于共产主义原则的一部分<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>因此没有向外发表<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>不过以此为收纳党员之标准<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这宣言之中文原稿不能在此地找到<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>所以兄弟把它从英文稿翻译出来<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>决定这宣言之时间既然有一年多了<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>当然到现在须要有修改和添补的地方<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>我很希望诸位同志把这个宣言仔细研究一番<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>因为每个共产主义者都要注意这种重要的文件一一共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>并且会提交远东人民会议中国代表团中之共产主义者组讨论<SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; .</SPAN>讨论结果将要供中国共产党的参<SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</SPAN>考和采纳<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp; chang&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>一九二一年十<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2009\" Month=\"2\" Day=\"10\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">二月十日</st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp; \"<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">姓张的译者是谁呢<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>出席远东人民代表大会的中国代表团中有两位姓张的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>要么是张太雷<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>要么是张国焘<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他们英语都好<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>但根据<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>兄弟<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>这一口语<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>可断定由张国焘译出可能性最大<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>张国焘说话处事较圆滑<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>常用<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>兄弟<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>口语<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">如果推论一下<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp; &lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>可能是这样流传的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.1920</SPAN>年夏天筹备建党<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>第一次会没开成不欢而散<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>第二次会<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>陈独秀等<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>人决定建党<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>并由<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>人起草党纲<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>大家通过<SPAN lang=EN-US>,.</SPAN>后来<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>人正式成立中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>在李大钊张申府定下党名叫中国共产党之后<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>由张申府给陈独秀回信<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>说明党名叫中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>紧接着就是起草党的宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>,11</SPAN>月份写成<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>交给了维经斯基<SPAN lang=EN-US>..</SPAN>维经斯基把<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>带回苏俄<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>可是<SPAN lang=EN-US>1922</SPAN>年张国焘到了伊尔库茨克<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中文和俄文稿的<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>找不到<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>自己手中也没有<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; ,</SPAN>怎么办<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>况且参加<SPAN lang=EN-US>1922</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月下旬的远东人民会议又急须此宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>于是张国焘就在<SPAN lang=EN-US>1921</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>曰前译了英译本<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.</SPAN>并就此情况加了一段说明<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">张国焘译的<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党宣言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;,</SPAN>是中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立的原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立的标志<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>它的内容分三章<SPAN lang=EN-US>:&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>笫一<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>共产主义者的理想是实现生产资料共有制<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>第二<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>党的目的是建立新社会<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>第三<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>党的纲领是消灭资本主义制度<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>以革命手段打倒资本家国家<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>建立无产阶级专政的国家<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>坚持无产阶级专政<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>走出一条到达共产主义的道路<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这个宣言在当时水平很高<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>真正了解了共产国际<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>态度上坚决跟着共产国际<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4,1920</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>曰陈独秀发表<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;&lt;</SPAN>共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>月刊短言<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&lt;4&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">此文是中国共产党党刊<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>的发刊词<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>虽未署名<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>但都知是陈独秀所写<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&lt;&lt;</SPAN>共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>月刊创刊号发行这天<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>安排在俄国<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>十月革命<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>节日子<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是有意表明中国共产党坚决走<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>十月革命<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>之路<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>发行此月刊就是高举十月革命的旗帜<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>月刊创刊号及其发刊词都是<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年建党的原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>是中国共产党于<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立的又一个标志<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.&nbsp; 1921</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月张太雷<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>关于建立共产国际远东书记处中国支部的报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&lt;5&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1921</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月张太雷受中国共产党指派<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>随同维经斯基到伊尔库茨克共产国际远东书纪处工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他们来这里之前<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>这里不叫共产国际远东书亡记处<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这里原是俄共<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>布<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>西伯利亚局东方民族处<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他们来向共产国际远东书记处报到<SPAN lang=EN-US>.,</SPAN>这个处工作内容没什么改变<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>机构设置须要完善<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>张太雷便打了个报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>要求建立远东书记处中国支部<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>结果得到批准<SPAN lang=EN-US>.,</SPAN>建立远东书记处中国科<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>维经斯基与张太雷同被任命为中国科的书记<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r[FS:PAGE]\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">张太雷在这个请示报告中说<SPAN lang=EN-US>:\"</SPAN>中国共产党代表张太雷于<SPAN lang=EN-US>1921</SPAN>年春天到达伊尔库茨克<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>为了与远东书记处建立更密切的联系<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>书记处指示他准备一个报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>并在即将于莫斯科举行的共产国际第三次大会上提交出来<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>中国共产党另一位代表杨和德<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>音<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>也到了伊尔库茨克<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这两个中国人和远东书记处代表举行多次会议<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>决定建立共产国际远东书记处中国支部<SPAN lang=EN-US>\",\"</SPAN>这个支部本身隶属于远东书记处<SPAN lang=EN-US>\",\"</SPAN>中国支部也隶属于共产国际组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>因此中国共产党中央委员会和共产国际远东书记处之间的关系<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>也必须遵循同样的组织联系原则<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>即远东书记处中国支部的全部成员应由驻远东书记处的中国共产党中央委员会所属的各地区代表组成<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">张太雷这个报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>主要讲中国共产党与远东书记处与共产国际的组织关系<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>确定这种最初的党际关系的报告及批复<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>都属于原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>它证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中国共产党在第一次全国代表大会召开前<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>己经被共产国际承认<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>中共中央的代表已经在共产国际东方书记处工作了<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1921</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共产党第一次全国代表大会<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&lt;6&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">这个文献是中国共产党第一次全国代表大会结束后<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中共中央向共产国际的报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>落款没有标明时间<SPAN lang=EN-US>.1929</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>31</SPAN>曰董必武致何叔衡信中<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>说他与李汉俊起草了这个报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>会上通过的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>但文件并没有说中共一大是党的成立大会<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>文件第一行就写<SPAN lang=EN-US>:\"</SPAN>中国的共产主义组织是去年年中成立的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>起初在上海<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>该组织只有<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>个人<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>领导人是有威望的<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>新青年<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>主编陈同志<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这个组织逐渐扩大其活动范围<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>现在己有六个小组五十三个成员<SPAN lang=EN-US>.\"</SPAN>这个文件是中国共产党原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>它承认党是<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年年中成立的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>我们看到<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>尽管语词表述上有羞羞打打迹象<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>出于迎合共产国际<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>但总的说<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>文件己肯定共产主义组织是<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年夏成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有领袖<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有队伍<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有政治活动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>是个政党组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>它肯定了党在<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年己是客观存在<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">以上<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>笔者引用了<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>个中共<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立的原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这些文献告诉我们<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中国共产党是<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年正式成立的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有组织有队伍有领袖有纲领有宣言有党刊<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>并得到上级党共产国际的承认和领导<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这一切证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立是完全符合政党成立标准的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">三<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>国际共产主义运动实践的证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1920</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年中国共产党成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>马上获得共产国际的承认<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>中国共产党登上了国际共产主义运动的政治舞台<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>笔者列以下根据作以考证<SPAN lang=EN-US>,<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1,<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1920\" Month=\"8\" Day=\"17\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1920<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年8</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月17</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&lt;&lt;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">维经斯基给俄共<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>布<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>中央西佰利亚局东方民族处的信<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&lt;7&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">维经斯基亲历中国共产党<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年夏成立的过程<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>而且是指导者<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>所以他这封信<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>也属中共成立的原始档案文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>并且是对<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立中国共产党的权威性的认证<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">维经斯基信中说<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>他在上海逗留的工作成果是<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>建立了上海革命局<SPAN lang=EN-US>\",&nbsp; </SPAN>由<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>人组成<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>除了他还有<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>个中国人<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>革命局下设几个部<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>对这个革命局怎么理解呢<SPAN lang=EN-US>?</SPAN>我们从根上说起<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1920</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>俄共<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>布<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>远东区负责人库什纳利克夫和妇女委员萨赫雅诺娃<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>给俄共中央写信<SPAN lang=EN-US>,&nbsp; </SPAN>要求与中国革命建立经常的联系<SPAN lang=EN-US>.3</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>俄共中央批准建立远东局<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>负责人换成西比利亚克夫<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>远东局在海参崴设立分局<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>不久<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>由俄共中央与共产国际联系并获批准<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>由海参崴分局派一小组<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>前往中国<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>任务是同中国革命组织建立联系<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>组长维经斯基<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>翻译杨明斋<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>俄藉华人<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;,</SPAN>秘书马麦耶夫<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>还有维经斯基的夫人库兹涅佐娃<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>马麦耶夫的爱人兼打字员马麦耶娃<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>他们一行<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>人来华<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他们以<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>生活报<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>记者身份活动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>维经斯基到北京与李大钊讨论建党问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>接着<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>又带李大钊介绍信去上海找陈独秀<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>研究建党问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>一拍即合<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>于<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月正式筹备建党<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这就是维经斯基站在他那工作角度说的上海革命局<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">我们可以看出<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>这段时间<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>维经斯基不是为共产国际工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>而是为俄共远东局东方民族处及海参崴分局工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>几个月后<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>即<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>远东局改为西伯利亚局<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>仍设东方民族处<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这时维经斯基来华己四个月左右<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他也应当向西伯利亚局东方民族处的领导写信汇报一下在华工作了<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>于是就产生了<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1920\" Month=\"8\" Day=\"17\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>17</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>这封信<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>信中说的上海革命局<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是从东方民族处角度说的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>指包括他在内的中国共产党成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; 1921</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>俄共西伯利亚局东方民族处<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>改名为共产国际远东书纪处<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这开始维经斯基才是共产国际代表<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>但他这封信<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>确是<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年中国共产党成立的有力证据<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2,&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">中国共产党代表张太雷任共产国际远东书记处了中国科书记<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&lt;8&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1921\" Month=\"3\" Day=\"22\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1921<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年3</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月22</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate>,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">远东书记处会议记录<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>记下了张太雷任中国科书记的事实<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>张太雷的委任状<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>不是中国组织签发的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>而是共产国际远东书记处于<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1921\" Month=\"5\" Day=\"16\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>1921</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>16</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>签发的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&lt;9&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">张太雷的身份<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>道德<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>才能受到远东书记处的特别喜欢和重视<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp;</SPAN>张太雷<SPAN lang=EN-US>17</SPAN>岁考入北大法科<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>因家贫念不起转入天津北洋大学<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他担任学生会评议部部长<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>参加领导学生运动<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他英语好<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>一边念书一边打工<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>在<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>华北明星报<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;</SPAN>作英语翻译<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>因天津与北京的学生运动连成一片<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>张太雷结识了北大教授李大钊和柏烈威<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>俄人<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>教授<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他们都在维经斯基指导下工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>柏烈威在北京参加俄华通讯社<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>当社招聘翻译时张太雷受聘了<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>并与他们结为知已<SPAN lang=EN-US>.1920</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月李大钊介绍维经斯基去上海会见陈独秀<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>张太雷正好北洋大学毕业一同去了<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>拜访了陈独秀<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>不久回到北京加入中共北京支部<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>又回天津组织社会主义青年团<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>任团书纪<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1921\" Month=\"2\" Day=\"8\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1921<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年2</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月8</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US>张太雷突然收到李大钊的通知.</SPAN></SPAN>马上到北京再见李大钊和维经斯基<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>李大钊告诉他同维经斯基一起到共产国际远东书记处工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>到那不久被任为中国科书记<SPAN lang=EN-US>.1921</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>月俞秀松作为中共另一位正式代表来到远东书记处<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>张太雷仍任中国科书记并获了委任状<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">远东书记处领导人舒米亚茨基<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>非常喜欢中国这两位青年领袖人物<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>决定他们都参加<SPAN lang=EN-US>1921</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月莫斯科共产国际第三次大会<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>委托他们起草中国共产党向大会的报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>他们按时完成了<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>并在大会发了言<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>当然今天看这个报告水平并不高<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>因他们经历不广<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>无准备<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>手中资料不足<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>理应写进的时间和数字却没有写进<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>有些带盖摇<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>但不管有何漏洞<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>张太雷俞秀松作为出席共产国际第三次大会代表是真的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>张太雷被命为远东书记处中国科书记是真的<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>张太雷代表中共向大会作报告是真的<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>这证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年成立的中国共产党已获共产国际承认<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>已被各国共产党公认<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>中共在一大前就已经活动在国际共产主义运动实践中<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=宋体>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1921\" Month=\"5\" Day=\"4\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1921<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年5</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月4</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US>张太雷代表中共中央向朝鲜共产党成立大会祝词.&lt;10&gt;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1921</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">年初成立的共产国际远东书记处<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>下设中国<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>朝鲜<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>曰本和蒙藏四科<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>工作由书记舒米亚茨基统管<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>一党召开成立大会<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>自然分配别党帮忙<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>对朝鲜共产党成立大会张太雷不仅参加筹备<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>而且担任成立大会组织局成员<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1921\" Month=\"5\" Day=\"4\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1921<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年5</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月4</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate>,</SPAN>朝鲜共产党成立大会在伊尔库茨克举行<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>张太雷在大会上代表中共致词<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>他说<SPAN lang=EN-US>:&nbsp; \"</SPAN>我很荣幸以中共中央的名议在大会发言<SPAN lang=EN-US>.......,\"<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">这次祝词<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>在舒米亚茨基<SPAN lang=EN-US>1928</SPAN>年悼念张太雷的长篇文章中得到记载<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>舒米亚茨基当年不过<SPAN lang=EN-US>35</SPAN>岁<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>军人<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>久经考验的布尔什维克<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>远东书记处负责人<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>是张太雷的直接领导<SPAN lang=EN-US>.&nbsp; </SPAN>他的悼念文章<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;&lt;</SPAN>中国共青团史和共产党史片断一一悼念中国共青团和共产党组织者之一张太雷同志<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;,</SPAN>同样证明<SPAN lang=EN-US>1920</SPAN>年中国共产党已经成立<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>而且活动在国际共产主义运动政治舞台上<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>为各国共产党所公认<SPAN lang=EN-US>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4,&nbsp; <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1922\" Month=\"7\" Day=\"11\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\">1922<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年7</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月11</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US>马林&lt;&lt;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">给共产国际执行局的报告<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;&gt;.&lt;11&gt;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><S","title":"关于1920年成立中国共产党的考证","time":1266690552000}